<main class="page-content">

  <section>
    <!-- Swiper-->
    <div class="swiper-outer">
      <div data-simulate-touch="false" class="swiper-container swiper-slider">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
          <div data-slide-bg="<%= image_path 'index-02.jpg' %>" class="swiper-slide">
            <div data-caption-animate="fadeInUp" class="swiper-slide-caption">
              <h1>Athan Kaloidis Memorial</h1>
              <p class="big">The legacy of a great man, remembered through a charity golf tournament,
                <br class="veil reveal-xl-block"> supported by the many people who were touched by the life of Athan
                Kaloidis.
              </p>
              <% if signed_in? %>
                <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-white btn-sm">Register</a>
              <% else %>
                <a href="<%= donate_path %>" class="btn btn-white btn-sm">Donate</a>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div data-slide-bg="<%= image_path 'index-03.jpg' %>" class="swiper-slide">
            <div data-caption-animate="fadeInUp" class="swiper-slide-caption">
              <h1>Athan Kaloidis Memorial</h1>
              <p class="big">The legacy of a great man, remembered through a charity golf tournament,
                <br class="veil reveal-xl-block"> supported by the many people who were touched by the life of Athan
                Kaloidis.
              </p>
              <% if signed_in? %>
                <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-white btn-sm">Register</a>
              <% else %>
                <a href="<%= donate_path %>" class="btn btn-white btn-sm">Donate</a>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Swiper Pagination-->
        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
        <!-- Swiper Navigation-->
        <div class="swiper-button-prev mdi mdi-chevron-left"></div>
        <div class="swiper-button-next mdi mdi-chevron-right"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-10 section-md-30 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="shell text-xl-center offset-top-42">
      <h2>Athan Kaloidis Memorial Foundation, Inc.</h2>
      <hr class="divider divider-60 divider-primary offset-top-32">
      <div style="font-size: 1.4em">
        <p>
          The Athan Kaloidis Memorial Foundation, Inc. has been established to honor the life and legacy of Athan
          Kaloidis, a man who helped many and who's kindness touched many more. We hope that through this Foundation we can
          honor his memory by giving back to others.
        </p>
        <hr class="divider divider-60 divider-primary offset-top-32">
        <p>
          A memorial golf tournament is held every year in his honor. This year's tournament will be held August 27th at 'Watertown Golf Club'. This tournament has raised an excess of $50,000 for the Make-A-Wish Foundation of Connecticut. We hope that you will support us this year and help make a difference in the lives of children the Make-A-Wish
          Foundation helps.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for taking the time to visit the site. Should you have any questions about the foundation or the
          tournament, please do not hesitate to contact us
        </p>
        <h6>Thank You,</h6>
        <h6>The Kaloidis Family</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="section-60 section-md-20">
    <div class="shell shell-wide">
      <h2>Tournament</h2>
      <hr class="divider divider-40 divider-primary offset-top-32">
      <div class="range">
        <div class="cell-md-4 cell-sm-6">
          <div class="box-variant-1">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'icon-01.png' %>" alt="" class="img-responsive center-block">
            <h6 class="offset-top-22">18 holes</h6>
            <hr class="divider divider-gray divider-50">
            <p>Played shotgun style at <%= ApplicationHelper.tournament_venue %>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cell-md-4 cell-sm-6 offset-top-22 offset-sm-top-0">
          <div class="box-variant-1">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'icon-02.png' %>" alt="" class="img-responsive center-block">
            <h6 class="offset-top-22">Make-A-Wish Foundation</h6>
            <hr class="divider divider-gray divider-50">
            <p>All proceeds go to the Make-A-Wish foundation of Connecticut.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cell-md-4 cell-sm-6 offset-top-22 offset-md-top-0">
          <div class="box-variant-1">
            <img src="<%= image_path 'icon-03.png' %>" alt="" class="img-responsive center-block">
            <h6 class="offset-top-22">sponshorships available</h6>
            <hr class="divider divider-gray divider-50">
            <p>Advertise your company by purchasing a sponsorship</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-light">
    <div class="shell shell-wide section-top-60 section-md-top-0">
      <div class="range text-md-left">
        <div class="cell-xl-6 cell-md-7 cell-md-push-1">
          <img src="<%= image_path 'TheoAndEleni1_Medium.png' %>" alt="" class="img-responsive center-block"></div>
        <div class="cell-md-5 cell-xl-6">
          <h2>Maria Eleni Kaloidis and Athan</h2>
          <hr class="divider divider-primary divider-60 divider-offset divider-md-left">
          <div class="offset-md-top-42 offset-top-22 inset-xl-right-70">
            <p>Athan Kaloidis was the uncle to Maria Eleni Kaloidis. Athan loved Maria Eleni dearly, and ofcourse Maria Eleni loved him and will always cherish her uncles memory.<br><br> Tragically, Maria Eleni was diagnosed with Muscular Dystrophy a few months after she was born, confining her to a wheelchair for her entire life.<br><br> Eleni has worked very hard to stay healthy, and fights every day. When she was 9, the Make-A-Wish Foundation of Connecticut granted her wish and sent her to beautiful Orlando Florida - Disney World!!! <br><br>Because of what Make-A-Wish has done for Maria Eleni, and thousands of other kids around the world - The Athan Kaloidis Memorial Foundation Golf Tournaments proceeds will be donated, to the Make-A-Wish foundation of Connecticut.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="http://curesma.org/" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm offset-top-52">Visit CureSMA.org</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= render 'main/mini_gallery' %>

</main>